buildWrapper

public APIWrapper buildWrapper(City city,
                               EndpointType endpointType,
                               String apiKey,
                               NetworkManagerFactory networkManagerFactory)
                        throws APIWrapperException
Builds an APIWrapper. NOTE: This operation could require some time to be done (it involves network operations).

Parameters:
city - Desired city to work with.
endpointType - Type of the desired endpoint (useful if you need, for example, a dev one to test your application).
apiKey - Api key which allows to perform some operations. If you need one, go to the list of servers and request it.
networkManagerFactory - A NetworkManager instances builder.
Returns:
An instance suited to the given parameters.
Throws:
APIWrapperException - If there was any problem.
